query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND kt2.kind not in ('movie','video game','tv mini series','episode','tv series','video movie') AND kt1.kind in ('video movie','video game','tv mini series','episode','movie','tv movie') AND it2.info in ('LD label','death notes','filming dates','mini biography','votes','magazine cover photo','copyright holder','LD pressing plant','LD production country') AND mc2.note not like '%Canada%' AND mc2.note not like '%Denmark%' AND mc2.note not like '%Sweden%' AND mc2.note not like '%Mexico%' AND cn2.country_code not in ('pl','ge','qa','nc','sm','kw','ne','vn','gu','ly') AND mi_idx1.info < '10.0' AND t2.production_year > 2009 AND t2.production_year < 2012 AND it1.info not in ('LD disc size','LD year','LD official retail price','tech info','LD pressing plant','weekend gross','LD number of chapter stops','LD dynamic range','runtimes','LD release date','LD catalog number','soundtrack','LD additional information','where now','trade mark','LD quality program','keywords','LD review') AND cn1.country_code not in ('lv','xyu','tt','ai','sa','cd','mv')
